8) Report make, model and license plate of vehicle to agent;
9) Participate in vocational training while in the institution;
10) Seek/maintain employment of at least 30 hours per week;
11) Provide DNA sample (unless previously submitted) and pay the DNA surcharge on each count;
12) Pay all costs, fees and surcharges. Failure to pay will result in a civil judgment;

